=== Getting and setting priorities ===

These functions are used to manage the priority of a log category, which determines if a message
will be written to the log or not. For example if a category is set to SDL_LogWarn, only messages
of priority SDL_LogWarn, SDL_LogError and SDL_LogCritical will be written.

* [[SDL_LogSetAllPriority]]
